parameters:
\>Five years ago, I came from the Imperial Kingdom
to the Kingdom of Greatland.

\>Unfortunately, my parents were creeped out by
me, who had the unfortunate talent for magic,
using demonic powers.

\>In the Imperial Kingdom, there are hardly any
magicians.

According to the story, it seems that it's because
this land has little magical power.

And I ended up going to the magic-rich Kingdom of
Greatland.

\>One-way ticket. Moreover, I haven't even decided
which magic academy to enter.

\>It's not really an unusual story. Unless it's a
family that has a favorable view of magic, this is
how things usually go.

<x1>Entering a boarding magic academy is also a
possibility.
And I, ended up being stranded.
